---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Talks - Zeyu Li"
  description="Conference presentations and invited talks"
>
  <h1>Talks & Presentations</h1>
  <p class="page-intro">
    Selected presentations at conferences, seminars, and other academic venues.
  </p>

  <section class="talks-section">
    <h2>Invited Talks</h2>
    <ul class="talks-list">
      <li class="talk-item">
        <h3>Sustainable Materials for the Future</h3>
        <p class="talk-meta">MIT Materials Science Seminar • Cambridge, MA • March 2024</p>
        <p>
          Keynote presentation on developing sustainable alternatives to traditional materials 
          and their potential impact on environmental challenges.
        </p>
      </li>

      <li class="talk-item">
        <h3>Advances in Biocompatible Polymers</h3>
        <p class="talk-meta">Stanford Biomaterials Symposium • Stanford, CA • January 2024</p>
        <p>
          Overview of recent developments in biocompatible polymer design and their 
          applications in drug delivery systems.
        </p>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Conference Presentations</h2>
    <ul class="talks-list">
      <li class="talk-item">
        <h3>Novel Synthesis Methods for Nanomaterials</h3>
        <p class="talk-meta">Materials Research Society Fall Meeting • Boston, MA • December 2023</p>
        <p>Oral presentation on innovative approaches to nanomaterial synthesis.</p>
      </li>

      <li class="talk-item">
        <h3>Biomaterial-Cell Interface Characterization</h3>
        <p class="talk-meta">American Chemical Society National Meeting • San Francisco, CA • August 2023</p>
        <p>Poster presentation on advanced characterization techniques for biomaterial surfaces.</p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <style>
    h1 {
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    }

    .page-intro {
      font-size: 1.125rem;
      color: var(--color-text-secondary);
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2xl);
      max-width: 800px;
    }

    .talks-section h2 {
      margin-top: var(--spacing-2xl);
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
      color: var(--color-text);
    }

    .talks-list {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .talk-item {
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
      padding: var(--spacing-lg);
      background: var(--color-surface);
      border-radius: var(--border-radius-md);
      border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    }

    .talk-item h3 {
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
      color: var(--color-text);
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }

    .talk-meta {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--color-text-muted);
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .talk-item p:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
      color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
